n we went for our honeymoon to Bath - in the excitement of the moment I took - I ran away with my brother's straw hat. Yes, it was a better one than mine see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 What about housekeeping when you first set up home, would you give all your earnings to your wife?
