Well you see I - I can remember the time I thought about it, I thought about it a very long time. Yes. It's - it's a thing that you want to think a lot about. And it - it took us a long time - it took me a long time before I popped the question.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Did you actually pop the question and say, will you marry me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 
No. It came around gradually. At a specific time I must have said something to that - to that effect. But - nothing very - nothing dramatic, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Did it come as a surprise to her?
