\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Well, yes, I think so, it's only the - it's more of - I don't know what to say about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Did you have rings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 She had a ring, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 You bought her a ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Was there an announcement in the paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Or a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 You bought her ring after you told her parents you were getting married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 I don't remember telling her parents. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Not when you bought the ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 No. Nor I didn't - I'm sure I didn't tell my own parents either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 You just went and bought a ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Yes. That's the end of it. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Did our parents treat you differently once you were engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270513 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Could you come in later in the night?
