\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 Yes. Yes. In the - Frontier Street.
