\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10378257 WG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4263350\charrsid14304431 I think I take - took somebody's hat instead of my own.
